Why was I denied the memories of the terror of the night?<br>
Why is not the sound of my brothers pain, in my mind?<br><br>
Where was the doc, when Murphy got hit?<br><br>
Why did he cross in front of me?<br>
Why did the bullet find him instead?<br>
Where is his baby daughter today?<br><br>
It was just like in the John Wayne movies, the bullets in the sand.<br><br>
CORPSMEN! CORPSMEN! CORPSMEN UP!<br><br>
Shit Rahm, He's DEAD!<br>

